name: Medibuy.com
overview: As of January 1, 2003, Medibuy.com, Inc. was acquired by Global Healthcare Exchange, LLC. Medibuy.com, Inc. operates a business-to-business Internet marketplace for the purchase and sale of medical and non-medical products and services used by the healthcare industry. The company, through its Web site medibuy.com, offers an online marketplace, which facilitates buyers and sellers an exchange to conduct daily commerce and access the information relating to products, services, pricing, and market trends. It has strategic partnership with Premier, Inc.; HCA; Commerce One; Quovadx, Inc.; IPNet Solutions, Inc.; HIMSS; and HealthTrust Purchasing Group (HPG), L.P. Medibuy.com, Inc. was formerly known as HS.com, Inc. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Nashville, Tennessee.
